-- U.S. RESEARCH ROUNDUP-Avon, Coty Inc, Aegerion Pharmaceuticals
-- 
-- Fri Oct 31, 2014 05:44AM EDT
-- None



Oct 31 (Reuters) - Wall Street securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several U.S. companies, including Avon Products, Coty Inc and Aegerion Pharmaceuticals, on Friday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Avon Products Inc <AVP.N>: Stifel cuts to hold from buy * Coty Inc <Coty.N>: Stifel raises to buy from hold * Aegerion Pharmaceuticals <AEGR.O>, Cardinal Health <CAH.N>: Cowen & Leerink cuts target * Trupanion Inc <TRUP.N>: RBC, Stifel cuts price target on the stock   Following is a summary of research actions on U.S. companies reported by Reuters on Friday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.  * ACI Worldwide Inc <ACIW.O>: Wedbush cuts price target to $18 from $19; rating neutral * Aegerion Pharmaceuticals <AEGR.O>: Cowen cuts price target to $25 from $36; market perform * Aegerion Pharmaceuticals <AEGR.O>: Leerink cuts price target to $32 from $46; outperform * AMN Healthcare Services <AHS.N>: BMO raises price target to $20 from $15; outperform * Avon Products Inc <AVP.N>: Stifel cuts to hold from buy * Brightcove Inc <BCOV.O>: RBC cuts price target to $8 from $9; rating sector perform * Cardinal Health <CAH.N>: Cowen raises price target to $88 from $86; rating outperform * Cardinal Health <CAH.N>: Leerink raises price target to $94 from $84; rating outperform * Catamaran Corp <CTRX.O>: Cowen raises price target to $57 from $56; rating outperform * Cigna Corp <CI.N>: Citigroup raises price target to $98 from $83; rating neutral * Coty Inc <Coty.N>: Stifel raises to buy from hold * Diebold Inc <DBD.N>: Wedbush cuts price target to $36 from $38; rating neutral * Expedia Inc <EXPE.O>: RBC raises price target to $95 from $90; rating sector perform * Fluor Corp <FLR.N>: Stifel cuts price target to $86 from $91; rating buy * FMC Corp <FMC.N>: Susquehanna cuts price target to $65 from $75; rating neutral * Groupon Inc <GRPN.O>: RBC raises price target to $7 from $6; rating sector perform * LinkedIn Corp <LNKD.N>: Stifel raises price target to $260 from $250; rating buy * LPL Financial <LPLA.O>: UBS cuts price target to $42 from $53; rating neutral * Microchip Technology <MCHP.O>: Credit Suisse raises target to $47.50 from $45; outperform * Mylan Inc <MYL.O>: Leerink raises price target to $62 from $55; rating outperform * Post Properties Inc <PPS.N>: Stifel raises price target to $58 from $56; rating buy * Quintiles <Q.N>: Jefferies raises price target to $58 from $56; rating hold * Spansion Inc <CODE.N>: Jefferies cuts price target to $24 from $25; rating buy * Trupanion Inc <TRUP.N>: RBC cuts price target to $13 from $14; rating outperform * Trupanion Inc <TRUP.N>: Stifel cuts price target to $16 from $18; rating buy * Westport Innovations <WPRT.O>: JP Morgan cuts price target to $7 from $8.50; neutral * Xcel Energy Inc <XEL.N>: BMO raises price target to $32 from $30; rating market perform